        <p class="metadata">Posted by Matthew Weier O'Phinney (matthew) on 2012-05-27T21:55:29.000+0000</p> 
        <div class="body">
            <p>Zend\Form was completely re-written for beta4. There is no translation awareness, as the Form component is simply a bridge between model (specifically, filtering, via the new InputFilter component) and view. If you need to translate labels or other form-related output, this should be done in the view layer. We could potentially make the various form view helpers translation aware for this purpose -- but, again, this would be in the view layer, not in the Form component itself.</p>

        </div>
